 live near Carcassonne in Aude High costs could prove barrier to widespread installation of the technology The index tracks key areas to 'compare how inequalities affect our lives' The 108 medicines are considered to pose risks that outweigh the benefits The new system will help to educate drivers, officials believe Rules for self-employed workers are different than for employees Subscribe to The Connexion See prices & plans HELP GUIDES Income Tax in France Healthcare in France Inheritance Law and Wills in France Visas and residency cards for France\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 6119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4294, \"end\": 4302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.760276555384494e-14, \"text\": \"Brittany\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany\"}, {\"begin\": 4382, \"end\": 4394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abies_nordmanniana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nordmann fir\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abies_nordmanniana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abies_nordmanniana\"}, {\"begin\": 4398, \"end\": 4411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Picea_abies\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Norway spruce\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Picea_abies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Picea_abies\"}, {\"begin\": 4650, \"end\": 4656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.014690894664115e-27, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4812, \"end\": 4826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cambell\", \"score\": 0.9999999997580744, \"rank\": 8.376671649906056e-11, \"text\": \"James Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc